              51-67.</li>
            <li>Schnyder, U., Schnyder-Luthi, C., Ballinari, P., &amp; Blaser, A. (1998). Therapy for vaginismus: In vivo versus in vitro desensitization. <em>Can J Psychiatry, 43</em>(9), 941-44.</li>
          </ol>
                  

                      
